Sample Twitter client that uses Twitter4J library (http://twitter4j.org) to integrate Twitter in Android applications.

Request for contribution
======
The code may be buggy, of low quality, but that's because I wanted to make easy to understand.
The UI is shabby.

But the bright side, you can help in improving all this.
Fork it, improve it, and push back. I'll be happy!
But just don't forget to credit accordingly.

Enjoy!
